        <abstract> 
<p>Suspects that the reported skeleton of a tailed man is that of some distinct animal [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10432</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Amused by brief visit of strange man about whom RB had written.</p>
            <p>Hopes that geology continues to flourish in Canada.</p>
